This ticket is partially resolved and partially irrelevant:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Since move to 'ckan2' in Jan 07 (&lt;a class="missing changeset" title="No default repository defined"&gt;r54&lt;/a&gt; onwards) have had tag support.
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Since move to versioned system (&lt;a class="missing changeset" title="No default repository defined"&gt;r121&lt;/a&gt; and ff.) have allowed tags to be added and amended by anyone.
